      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIR RICO (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (17.08) in a Grade 5 at this track. Better than last start and worth following up. HAYDEN'S MILK (5) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (22.81) at Murray Bridge. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ECHO MISS (1) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 300m behind Stifler (17.28) in a Invitation. Form from her last run is proving strong. Warrants plenty of respect. ONE MARGARITA (3) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when third (17.00) in a Grade 6 over 300m at Murray Bridge.",
